---
/** Cómo funciona + FAQ (dos columnas). */
---
      <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
        <div
          data-landing-reveal
          style="--lr-delay: 50ms"
          class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/75 dark:bg-gray-950/65 p-7 shadow-sm"
        >
          <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.howTitle">Cómo funciona</h2>
          <div class="mt-5 space-y-3" style="overflow-anchor: none;">
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 p-4">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none">
                <span data-i18n="landing.how1Summary">1) Define tecnologías</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.how1Body">SQL, Tableau, Python… tu mapa base.</p>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 p-4">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none">
                <span data-i18n="landing.how2Summary">2) Añade conceptos</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.how2Body">
                Lo que realmente aprendes dentro de cada tecnología.
              </p>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 p-4">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none">
                <span data-i18n="landing.how3Summary">3) Crea proyectos y evidencias</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.how3Body">
                URLs (enlace o embed), tecnologías, conceptos, rol y resultado.
              </p>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 p-4">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none">
                <span data-i18n="landing.how4Summary">4) Publica portfolio</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.how4Body">
                Tarjetas claras, filtro por tecnología y evidencia principal destacada.
              </p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          data-landing-reveal
          style="--lr-delay: 90ms"
          class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/75 dark:bg-gray-950/65 p-7 shadow-sm"
        >
          <h2 class="m-0 text-lg font-semibold" data-i18n="landing.faqTitle">Preguntas frecuentes</h2>
          <div class="mt-5 space-y-3" style="overflow-anchor: none;">
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 p-4">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none">
                <span data-i18n="landing.faq1Q">¿Por qué solo por invitación?</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.faq1A">
                Para iterar sin fricción y cuidar la experiencia mientras el producto crece con cabeza.
              </p>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 p-4">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none">
                <span data-i18n="landing.faq2Q">¿Qué es público hoy?</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.faq2A">
                Esta landing, la demo y la página de precios orientativa. La app completa necesita sesión.
              </p>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 p-4">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none">
                <span data-i18n="landing.faq3Q">¿Cómo pido acceso?</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.faq3A">
                Usa “Solicitar acceso” y cuenta tu caso. Respondemos cuando haya hueco.
              </p>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-xl border border-gray-200/80 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/60 dark:bg-gray-950/40 p-4">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 focus:outline-none">
                <span data-i18n="landing.faq4Q">¿Qué sigue en desarrollo?</span>
                <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform">⌄</span>
              </summary>
              <p class="mt-2 mb-0 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400" data-i18n="landing.faq4A">
                Todo lo de la hoja de ruta de abajo: enlaces públicos de portfolio, CV con export, salidas profesionales, flujo diario más mullido y cobros de verdad. Lo iremos contando cuando merezca la pena.
              </p>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>